---
import KvBanner from './KvBanner.astro';
---

<section id="eligibility" class="pt-0">
  <KvBanner color="sand" title="Eligibility & Submission Standards"/>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 overlap-wrap pb-16">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who can nominate</h3><p class="text-sm">Nomination of individuals must be submitted by an organisation including governments, intergovernmental organisations, business entities, academic institutions, non-governmental organisations, and other relevant stakeholders</p></div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who can be nominated</h3><p class="text-sm">Nominees must be a citizen of Southeast Asian countries (any of the 10 ASEAN Member States)</p></div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Language & format</h3><p class="text-sm">Submissions must be submitted in English and through the online application form with the required supporting documents and materials (including reports, books, links to visuals, articles, etc.)</p></div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200"><h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Integrity & ethics</h3><p class="text-sm">Unethical behaviour (misleading information or undue pressure) may result in disqualification and/or revocation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>